Joseph Akinwale Akinfenwa-Donus (amụrụ na 21 Mee 1997), nke a maara dịka Joeboy, bụ onye Naijiria na-agụ egwu na onye na-ede egwu. Maazị Eazi nke labelụ "emPawa Africa" chọpụtara ya n'afọ 2017
Ụdị egwu ya bụ nke Afro pop na R&B
A mụrụ ya na Lagos State, Nigeria.

Maazị Eazi nyere aka na egwu "Fààjí" na Ọktoba 26, 2018; o jiri akụkụ ya nke onyinye ọ natara n'aka emPawa100 gbaa vidiyo maka egwu ahụ. E wepụtara egwu Joeboy "Baby" na Machị 1, 2019; ọ nwetara nde iri abụọ na YouTube na Spotify na 2019. Vidio egwu ọhụụ maka "Baby" karịrị nde mmadụ iri atọ na otu na YouTube. Joeboy wepụtara egwu Killertunes mepụtara "Beginning" na August 15, 2019
Vidio egwu ọhụụ maka "Malite" karịrị nde mmadụ iri abụọ na atọ na YouTube

N'ime ya, ọ na-ahụ onwe ya ka ọ na-enwe mmetụta maka enyi ya nke ọ jụrụ na mbụ. Joeboy wepụtara egwu izizi ya bụ Love & Light na Nọvemba 2019. Ọ bụ emPawa Africa wepụtara ya ma ndị otu "Baby" na "Beginning" kwadoro ya. EP ahụ nwekwara egwu Mayorkun nyere aka "Don't Call Me" na "All for You".

Joeboy meriri Best Artiste na African Pop na 2019 All Africa Music Awards, na Best Pop na 2020 Soundcity MVP Awards Festival. A họpụtara ya maka ọtụtụ City People Entertainment Awards na The Headies Joeboy wepụtara egwu Dera mepụtara "Call" na Eprel 10, 2020. A kọwara ya dị ka "abụ ịhụnanya na-adọrọ adọrọ", "Call" bụ egwu mbụ sitere na abọm studio mbụ ya na-abịanụ
Vidio TG Omori duziri maka "Call" nwere isiokwu dystopian sci-fi.
